title: Style Transfer of Images and Videos
description: Two versions of PyTorch implementations of style transfer which can learn from existing artistic styles and generate new visually pleasing results. Version 2 enables fast transformation of high-resolution images and videos on GPU.

title: Brazilian E-Commerce Rating Prediction
description: A big data project that uses a large e-commerce dataset to predict customers' review ratings. Detailed EDA, feature engineering, and modeling are included.

title: Automating Stock Trading with Reinforcement Learning
description: A ML project that studies the problem of automated stock trading using reinforcement learning. It leverages a deep reinforcement learning library to simulate a stock market environment and train an agent to maximize the return of a stock portfolio.

title: Kaggle: Google Landmark Recognition 2021
description: A competition about labeling landmarks in images. Awarded Silver Medal. Ranked top 10%.

title: Kaggle: Google Smartphone Decimeter Challenge
description: A competition about enhancing accuracy of GPS positioning. Awarded Bronze Medal. Ranked top 10%.

title: GoGreen
description: A data-centric web application that increases people's awareness of environmental issues and promotes eco-friendly transportation.

title: AlphaGame
description: AI agents trained with 2 algorithms to make smart decisions in 3 games, Snake, Pong, and Flappy Bird.

title: CarSpeech
description: Built convolutional neural network models using Tensorflow to classify important words in human speech from the AVICAR dataset recorded in vehicles.

title: Student Evaluation System
description: A software that enables students to fill out peer reviews online and then aggregates the results for instructors.
